      <H2>MOTORS</H2></FONT>
      <P><FONT class=3Dintro face=3DArial,Verdana,SanSerif =
size=3D2><B>Electric=20
      motors, both ac and dc types, come in many shapes and sizes. Some =
are=20
      standardized versions for general-purpose applications. Others are =

