  <TR>
    <TD><FONT class=3Dbody face=3DArial,Verdana,SanSerif><B>Motor=20
      efficiency:</B><BR>Small universal motors have an efficiency of =
about 30%,=20
      while 95% efficiencies are common for three-phase machines. In=20
      less-efficient motors, the amount of power wasted can be reduced =
by more=20
      careful application and improved motor design.=20
      <P>Motor efficiency also depends on actual motor load versus rated =
load,=20
      being greatest near rated load and falling off rapidly for under =
and=20
      overload conditions. =
</FONT></P></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE></BODY></HTML>
